snippet.title: World Without Reason - Reality 47
snippet.description:
In a perfect world devoid of any strife, a sad girl named Alexandra 47 gets abducted, is given almighty powers, and begins a tragedy that eclipses the entire universe.

World Without Reason releases at the end of this August!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2811960/World_Without_Reason/

#WorldWithoutReason #RenPy #indiegame #visualnovel
